(see [[1994 in music]]). ==Track listing== All songs by Ani DiFranco. #"Buildings and Bridges" – 4:05 #"Out of Range" (acoustic) – 3:46 #"Letter to a John" – 3:48 #"Hell Yeah" – 5:01 #"How Have You Been" – 4:29 #"Overlap" – 3:44 #"Face Up and Sing" – 2:53 #"Falling Is Like This" – 3:01 #"Out of Range" (electric) – 3:25 #"[[You Had Time]]" – 5:49 #"If He Tries Anything" – 3:15 #"The Diner" – 4:39 ==Personnel== *Ani DiFranco – [[Steel-string guitar|acoustic guitar]], [[percussion instrument|percussion]], [[piano]], [[electric guitar]], [[steel guitar]], [[vocals]] *Colleen Allen – [[saxophone]] *[[Chris Brown (Canadian singer)|Chris Brown]] – piano *Stephen Donald – [[trombone]] *Scot Fisher – [[accordion]] *Alisdair Jones – [[bass guitar|bass]] *[[Sarah McElcheran]] – [[trumpet]] *[[Andy Stochansky]] – [[dumbek]], [[drum kit|drums]], [[backing vocals]] ==Production== *[[record producer|Producers]] – Ani DiFranco, Ed Stone *[[audio engineer|Engineer]] – Ed Stone *[[art director|Art direction]] – Ani DiFranco *[[Design]] – Ani DiFranco *[[Photography]] – Scot Fisher ==References== {{Reflist}} {{Ani_DiFranco}} [[Category:Ani DiFranco albums]] [[Category:1994 albums]]
